com.energyxxer.commodore.item

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.energyxxer.commodore.item.Item

  • public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
    Defines an item of a specific type, complete with NBT data, which can be used with commands to give, clear, replace and test.
    See Also:
    Type, ItemType, TagCompound
